<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, January 6 (Xinhua) -- Russia does not agree to settle
the Georgian-Abkhazian conflict by using military forces, Russian
Foreign Ministry spokesman Gennady Tarasov said on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
