their assessed contribution to the United Nations, the release
said.
</P>
<P>
The outstanding contribution to the United Nations is over 3.1
billion U.S. dollars, of that amount roughly 1.6 billion is for
the regular budget, and over 1.5 billion for peacekeeping. 
