<HEADLINE> Chinese Bank Benefits from Stable Operation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, January 7 (Xinhua) -- Stable operation has enabled
the Fujian Industrial Bank, located in east China's Fujian
Province, to grow into a powerful regional bank, according to
official sources.
</P>
