<HEADLINE> Share Prices Continue to Decline on Singapore Market </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, January 7 (Xinhua) -- Share prices continued to
decline sharply on the Singapore market as the benchmark Straits
Times Industrials Index lost 71.06 points to close at 1,368.06
points on Wednesday, hitting the lowest level in five years.
