Nigerian Tribune
</P>
<P>
-- The first quarter allocation for Nigeria's 1998 budget is
to be released next week, a sharp contrast as the delay last
year, because the Abacha administration has only nine months
before handing over the civil rule in October, according to the
finance minister. 
</P>
