<TEXT>
<P>
SAN JOSE, January 6 (Xinhua) -- Presidents from Central
American countries will meet twice this month in Honduras to
inaugurate the headquarters of the Central American Bank of
Integration (CABI) and to attend the inaugural ceremony of the new
Honduran President.
</P>
