<TEXT>
<P>
RABAT, January 6 (Xinhua) -- Joan Roma and Bruno Saby lead the
way in the Paris-Dakar rally after Tuesday's sixth stage, a 354km
run from Ouarzazate to Smara, Morocco.
</P>
